Or in good groups the master looter has funded gem costs BEFORE splitting plat.<br>
<br>
In general I've cast peridot symbol for main warrior and chanter if we are in a difficult place; additionally, smaller symbols for other melees if we are in a really difficult place.  Otherwise I haven't ever really needed to symbol.  I tend to watch how fights are going in order to determine what we need.  Having symbol and higher HPs on people make CH more efficient and gives the cleric a bit of space to cast heals.<br>
